has led to a shift of the behavior

19:28.560 --> 19:31.440
towards targeting things that are so far,

19:31.440 --> 19:32.400
at least for me,

19:32.400 --> 19:34.800
from what most of us would think is valuable

19:34.800 --> 19:36.240
in a romantic relationship,

